Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约城已陷入黑暗两小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Two hours have passed since the city of New York plunged into darkness.
