Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对美国政府的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of the United States government.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Court is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也有毙了这家伙的冲动不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Anyone else want to shoot this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个旧法院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's an old courthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有人认出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Someone'll recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半城人都在街上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Half the city is out in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是不能审问他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I guess we're not gonna question them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're Decima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定开口前就先跳楼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They'll go out a window before they'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们快走吧  免得他同伙赶到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's get out of here before anymore of 'em show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得阻止审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We got to stop that trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们被控背叛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You stand accused of betraying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}your fellow citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被控将我们的民主\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Of trading in our democracy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了极权\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}for a police state,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们煞费苦心  给你们一个公平的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And we've taken great pains to give you a fair trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为尊重你们的辩护权\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}To honor your right to counsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们请来了全市最优秀的辩护律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we've brought in the best defense attorney in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保证能有一个公平的裁决\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}To ensure an equitable verdict right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们挑了你们的同类当陪审团\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we've selected a jury of your peers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于新闻自由对民主至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And since a free press is vital in every democracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们邀请了媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we've invited the media...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  快点  坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Keep moving. Come on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这场诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and opened up these proceedings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向全世界公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to observers around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边信号如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How's that signal down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星上行线路很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Satellite uplink is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在向全世界现场直播\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're streaming live all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千两百万观众  数量还在增加\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}12 million viewers and counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们的指控非常严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, the charges against you are grave:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三亿一千三百万项\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}313 million counts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非法窃听罪  同谋罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of illegal wiretapping, plus conspiracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间谍罪  以及叛国罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}espionage, and treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后两项是死刑罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The last two are punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有些人  被我们抓获现形\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Some of you, we have dead to rights;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而其他人  事实略不清晰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}others, the facts are less clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要是有人想招供自己的罪状\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So anyone who's willing to confess their crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并指证其他同谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and testify against their co-conspirators
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会获得宽大处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}will be granted leniency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己选\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控方传唤曼纽・里维拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The prosecution calls Manuel Rivera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你的律师  我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As your attorney, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  哈罗德  我不会说出你的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't worry, Harold, your secret's safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可就不一定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not so sure about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给一堆人看过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Must have shown the photo to a dozen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能认出这个法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nobody seems to recognize the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得马上找到线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need a lead fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"又扮法官又扮陪审团\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}With Vigilance playing judge and jury,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离扮处决人果断不远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}executioner won't be far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五分钟内赶去第五大道和23街的交叉口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Be at the intersection of 5th and 23rd in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Good-bye, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  根  就这样  你在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wait, Root, is that all? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我该在的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Right where I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到它了  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You found it, didn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找到哈罗德了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Did you find Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很担心他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在找\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're working on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的  你真的准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but seriously, are you about to kamikaze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟群书呆子一起闯德西玛堡垒找死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}into a Decima fortress with a bunch of nerds?
