Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想表现公平审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You want the appearance of a fair trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少装腔作势\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bottle the histrionics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陈述你的检控吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Present your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控方传唤参议员罗斯・加里森\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}People call Senator Ross Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面就是23街和第五大道交叉口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's 23rd and 5th up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根让我们来是为了  自行车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Root sent us here for bikes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警察  放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}NYPD. Drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手举起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hands where I can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  小熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get off, Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这儿干嘛呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚有疯子抢了个孩子的自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Some nutjob just jacked a kid on a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是你们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I thought you were looters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来得正好  莱奈尔  -你认识这家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Nice ride, Lionel. - You know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从停电后就没见着你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I haven't seen you since the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找到我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How'd you find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这狗跑到警局里  带了那飞越疯人院的口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dog showed up at the precinct with a message from Cuckoo's Nest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让来这交叉口会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to meet at this intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道她是要我来见你和这家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Didn't know she meant you and this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"造成的停电\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance caused the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们私设法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They set up a kangaroo court
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对付所有与机器有关的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to go after anyone tied to the Machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得找到哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We got to go find Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在直播审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're streaming the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警局查出来源没\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}NYPD know where from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被停电搞得手忙脚乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're kind of busy with the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五大道好多人打砸抢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We got a bunch of guys smashing up 5th avenue, looting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群戴着面具的暴徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bunch of jackasses running around in masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声东击西  是"时刻警惕"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Diversion tactic, Vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如在这街区转一圈吧  莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why don't you take a lap around the block, Lionel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们得去街对面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'Cause we're gonna need some gear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家运动品商店搞点装备\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}from that sporting goods store up the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是纽约警察在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It'd probably be best if the NYPD isn't around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便我们打砸抢啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when we smash in the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(287.099,180.937)\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&H01008F&\fs8.5}操作冲突\N连接不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又运来七台服务器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got seven more servers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫描一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's get them scanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这批货晚了两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This shipment's two days late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where the hell have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,策划这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Planning this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来某人爬山涉水而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like someone crawled in under the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认吧  你担心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Admit it, you were worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是担心任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm worried about the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟和赫什在想办法救芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Reese and Hersh are trying to save Finch,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是"撒马利亚人"把咱全杀掉就白费了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but that won't matter if Samaritan kills us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始干活吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩儿的是这个啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's gonna be that kind of party, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛把标签植入人体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima tags its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有射频微芯片的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Anyone who doesn't have an RFID chip
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会轻易被认出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}will stick out like a sore thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好打针了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ready for your shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参议员  你否认了解"北极光"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Senator, you've denied any knowledge of Northern Lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的名字在这些文件里出现了三十七次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}yet your name appears in these documents some 37 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么解释这\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, how do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在网上看什么都当真\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe you shouldn't believe everything you read on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D7证物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Exhibit D7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们发现我们监视美国人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They find out we're spying on the American people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都得进监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we all go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否认  粉碎  销毁任何与"北极光"有关的资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Deny, shred, burn anything related to Northern Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它从未存在过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要重新回答吗  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You care to rephrase your answer, Senator?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是断章取义\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those comments were taken out of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thank you for protecting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不明原由\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Although I'm baffled as to why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原由就是我一切行动的原由  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The same reason I've done everything, Harold,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}for my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你死了可没法帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you can't help me if you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟"北极光"的研发毫无关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had nothing to do with the development of Northern Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介入时那东西已经建成运转了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Damn thing was up and running when I was read in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在收拾烂摊子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just got stuck with cleaning up the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不公平啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hardly seems fair
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因为别人的罪行而冒生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}your life should be in danger for someone else's misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你不是那个[男]人  那谁是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So if you're not the guy, who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责的原来并不是男人  对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It never was a guy that was in control, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以退下了  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You may step down, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意加入吗  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You care to join us, Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街景摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One street view cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不能拍摄街景了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's not viewing streets anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个街景车司机的表情太有趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The look on that driver's face was priceless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西里的硬件得值十万块\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got to be 100 grand worth of hardware in this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个搜索引擎当自己是国安局了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's getting to be you can't tell a search engine from the NSA.
