Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(182.59,163.271)\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HC9C38E&\fs12\b1\frx358\fry356\frz332}短信\N未知\N{\b0}\N暴政如同地狱  不会被轻易推翻\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h托马斯・潘恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔我一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Toss me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没看见我们的脸吧  你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't think he saw our faces, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚  我们除掉了一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tonight, we got one off the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  他们会再建一百个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tomorrow, they build 100 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿到硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We got the hard drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以编写一个病毒  感染全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Could write a virus, infect the whole fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他们一个补丁就解决了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, they'll just look for a patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法削弱数据挖掘  领域感知\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Doesn't put a dent in data mining, domain awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}都是获取用户隐私的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要打开眼界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to adjust our sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our sights?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一场信息战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is an information war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要对付的那些人  他们控制信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to go after the people who control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滥用信息  摧毁他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}abuse it, destroy people's lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受节制\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and answer to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到点子上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now you're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表态\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人代表着不义的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Someone who represents everything that's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失控的奥威尔式集权\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}with an unchecked Orwellian state.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们冲他们下手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And we put them in the crosshairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他们上一堂终生难忘的课\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and we teach them a lesson no one will forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能当庭确认这些文件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can you identify these documents for the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们从更简单的问题开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's start with something simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是"探索者"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is "Research"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里有超过三百页的文档\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have here more than 300 pages
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涉及非法窃听  非法审讯  及非法暗杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}documenting illegal wiretaps, interrogations, and assassinations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都由"北极光"实施\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}carried out by "Northern Lights"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其全部信息都来自所谓"探索者"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}all using information from something called Research,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且都是两周一周期\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and all from one two-week period.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,官僚机构的动作不可能那么快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, no bureaucracy moves that fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我重新问下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so let me rephrase the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"探索者"是一个自动系统吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is "Research" an automated system?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一台机器吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is it a machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为美国联邦政府正式官员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As a sworn officer of the U.S. government,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既不承认也不否认有关此事的任何问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can neither confirm nor deny anything pertaining to this matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对其他所有问题都作同样回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I will say the same damn thing to every other question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你用枪指着我的头  扣动扳机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}until the moment you put that gun to my head and pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\fscy110\c&H020807&\fs37\frx2\fry8\move(131.737,270.87,131,30,550,2356)}全\N员\N工\N必\N须\N扫\N描
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\b1\fscy110\c&H155157&\fs23\frx2\fry8\frz358.4\move(243.854,278.9,243.117,48.03,550,2356)}否则警报会响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事一完\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As soon as this is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上切掉胳膊里这破芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm cutting this stupid chip out of my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞我的  我就搞你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll do yours if you do mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好迎接真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ready for the moment of truth--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说是谎言了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or lies really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电脑最扯蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Computers can bite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么朝自己人开火啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's with the friendly fire, yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑偏了  傻逼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're off the map, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科利尔派我们来管管你  免得你搞砸计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Collier sent us here to rein you in before you screw up the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Courthouse is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该待在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're supposed to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引警察远离审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}drawing the cops away from the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  法庭在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, man, courthouse is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早上刚往那边送过健力士啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just delivered the Guinness this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚  好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so I'd know, wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找这个小混蛋找了一晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Been looking for this little bastard all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他归你了  我们要赶去法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's all yours. We're due in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已看过证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You have seen the proof
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明你们眼前的这个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that the woman before you was the ringleader
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是"北极光"犯罪组织的头目\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of a criminal organization called Northern Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们起诉她涉嫌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We've implicated her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草率处决十七名美国公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in the summary execution of 17 American citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这还只是已知的人数\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and those are just the ones we know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自始至终\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And through it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她都毫无悔意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}she shows no remorse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为她的沉默已是默认\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I think her silence speaks volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有审议时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Since we don't have time for deliberation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接投票表决\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we'll put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被告做无罪推定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The defendant is presumed innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中谁认为她有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who among you find her guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪审团认定被告有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jury finds the defendant guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判决立即执行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sentence to be carried out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[911事件]77航班撞上五角大楼时你在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where were you when flight 77 hit the pentagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可就在楼里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because I was inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背出伤员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I carried out the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掩盖尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I covered up bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那之后我每一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I have spent every day since
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在追杀肇事者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}putting bullets in the people responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和所有企图\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and in anyone else who even thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次袭击我们国家的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that they can do that to our country again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要毙了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You want to shoot me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我不得不监听几个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}because I had to tap a few phone calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浏览几封电邮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}read a few e-mails,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就放马过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then you go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之后记得调转枪口对着你自己  科利尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you better turn that gun on yourself next, Mr. Collier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你也一样违法无数\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}because you have broken just as many laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你我唯一的区别是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and the only difference is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会高裹美国国旗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't wrap myself up in the American flag
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广而告知我是英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and try to convince people that I was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你热爱国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I believe you love your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信最初的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I believe that when you started,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家认为你所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}people thought what you were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有必要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}made a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在做过头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But it's gone too far,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须停止了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and it has to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁造了机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}who built the machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它工作原理如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where is it located?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主控一切的女人不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The woman in charge of it all doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道  那谁知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If you don't know, who does?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人民意愿已定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The people have spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问的问题  我知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The questions you're asking, I know the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它是我造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because I built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人上交手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Everyone needs to turn in their phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要换联络方式了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're switching up communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再集合会面不安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's no longer safe for us to meet here as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's going on, Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全措施\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Security measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起  存储仓库\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}From now on, storage units
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用来传达信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}will only be used as message centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还当我们是民主的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I thought this was a democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们何不  -想投票决定吗  亚当斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Why don't we-- - Want to put it to a vote, Adams?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道我们到底在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I want to know what the hell we're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没收集政治家的情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}instead of just doxing another politician,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没对某个网站进行分布式拒绝服务攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}another DDoS attack on some intel site.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有何建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸点东西  杀点人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Blow something up, take someone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说要表态\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You wanted to make a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We are not terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:22:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对付特定的违法者  不能附带伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We target specific violators, no collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你建议我们对付谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who do you suggest we go after?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些像摧毁你哥哥一样摧毁他人的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}People who destroy lives, like they did to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}let's put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们需要个目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I say we name the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个人选\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是对付我哥哥的那种人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The kind of person who went after my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,录音中\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你还没蠢到戴窃听器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Knew you wouldn't be dumb enough to wear a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在文件里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's all in the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者不如你来告诉她  亚当斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or why don't you just tell her, Adams?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  是你  你是联调局的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My God, it's you. You're FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先是对付我哥哥  现在又来对付我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}First he went after my brother, now they're after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我不用再带面具了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I guess I don't need to wear the mask anymore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪儿弄来的  这是一派胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where did you get this? This is a bunch of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"暴政如同地狱  不会轻易被推翻"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"Tyranny like hell is not easily conquered."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"斗争愈艰难  胜利愈荣耀"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"The harder the conflict, the more glorious the triumph."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"太容易得到的东西  我们不会珍惜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"What we obtain too cheap, we esteem too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其价值  取决于为其付出的努力"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It is dearness only that gives everything value."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Especially life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个"表态"如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How's that for a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁想投票决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Anybody else want to put it to a vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机都放到桶里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Phones in the bucket,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这垃圾拖出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and take out this garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有很多事要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We've got a lot of work to do.
