Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就感觉你很特别  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had a feeling there was something special about you, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意告诉你任何你想知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm willing to tell you whatever you want to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你同意放过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but only if you agree to spare the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判室里的其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of everyone else in this courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放人之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Before we release anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得先听听你的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we need to hear your testimony first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.42,0:24:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2001年9月12号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}On September the 12th, 2001,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始编码一个复杂的监视系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I began coding in a complex surveillance system
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一系统多年被赋予了很多代号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that would be known by many code names over the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.02,0:24:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直叫它"机器"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}although I always just called it "the Machine."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(287.099,180.937)\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&H01008F&\fs8.5}操作冲突\N连接不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.35,0:24:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是"撒马利亚人"的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So this is Samaritan's brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.72,0:24:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.60,0:25:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞  你一插上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So what's the deal, you just plug 'em in,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.20,0:25:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"就熄灯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then it's lights out, Samaritan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.94,0:25:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.05,0:25:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两列没亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}These two rows didn't light up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.89,0:25:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些灯不亮是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those lights staying dark is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.61,0:25:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"的人工智能要开启\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan's A.I. won't get switched on
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要格里尔拿到政府信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}until Greer gets the government feeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些灯要是变蓝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those lights turn blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.67,0:25:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.24,0:25:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在沉睡的巨人腹中  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're inside a sleeping giant, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.17,0:25:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把它吵醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Try not to wake it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.51,0:25:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辆货车像是岗哨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That van's some type of guard post.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like we're getting warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.89,0:25:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"  六个全死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance, all six dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.77,0:25:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他们惹恼的不止我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess we're not the only ones these guys have pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是如何运作的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是谁抢先了一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who do you think beat us to the punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.73,0:25:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2005年二月\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}February of 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器得到了所需的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the machine's information was provided...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在看审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They were watching the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.97,0:25:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但服务器当时还在IFT公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Although the servers remained at IFT.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.22,0:26:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.58,0:26:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到2009年我们将它交给政府时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}By the time we turned it over to the government in 2009,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.15,0:26:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器已经阻止了54起恐怖袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the machine had helped stop 54 terrorist attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.09,0:26:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救了约四千人的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}saving an estimated 4,000 lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.01,0:26:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道它之后救了多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't know how many it's saved since.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.63,0:26:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以虽然"北极光"被关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So even though Northern Lights was shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.86,0:26:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的机器还在运行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}your machine was still operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.11,0:26:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它现在在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid not even I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.32,0:26:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有操作权限吗  能关掉它吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you have access to it? Can we turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.89,0:26:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要恐惧我的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You have nothing to fear from my system,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.38,0:26:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科利尔先生  我可以保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Collier, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.83,0:26:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请见谅我不能相信你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You'll forgive me if I don't take you at your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.89,0:26:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器只会给出号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The machine's only output is a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.94,0:26:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府只能得到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's all the government ever gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.44,0:26:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只会表示\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}just a nudge to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你们应该查下这里"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"there's something you should look at here,"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.60,0:26:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就要由我们来查明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and that's up to us to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.41,0:26:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以它把人定义为疑犯  做有罪推定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So it brands people as suspects, guilty until proven innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, not my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.82,0:26:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.99,0:26:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它必须是封闭系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It had to be a closed system.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.04,0:26:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这样才能保护人民的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was the only way to protect people's rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.99,0:26:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还指望我们相信你有一丝一毫在乎人民的权利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You expect us to believe you gave one thought about people's rights
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.34,0:26:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是为政府建造了大型的监视武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}as you were building the government a weapon of mass surveillance?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.62,0:26:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.44,0:26:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你说它是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What else would you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.24,0:27:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会说  它是竭尽我全力的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I would call it the best I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.84,0:27:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就从来没想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And it never occurred to you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.95,0:27:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意造成的伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the damage this thing could do,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.93,0:27:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它摧毁的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the lives it could destroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想过  从第一天就想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It occurred to me on day one,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.28,0:27:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科利尔先生  之后的每一天都想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Collier, and every day since.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.21,0:27:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If you're asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.42,0:27:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己的作品是否感觉不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}if I feel at ease with what I've created,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.53,0:27:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这件事是对是错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or whether it was the right or the wrong thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.36,0:27:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I honestly don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.72,0:27:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我建造机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I designed the machine
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.74,0:27:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部分原因是我担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in part because I was worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.71,0:27:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直担心  其他人会造出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I remain worried, about what someone else might build...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.76,0:27:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他不担心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Someone who wasn't worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.86,0:27:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独裁没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nothing wrong with a dictatorship,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.50,0:27:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你是独裁者就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so long as you're the dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.83,0:27:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话讲完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I rest my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.39,0:27:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要投票吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Shall we put it to a vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.14,0:27:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥官  有人袭击了我们一个岗哨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Command, one of our guard posts has been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.72,0:27:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人生还  重复  无人生还\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No survivors, repeat, no survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.52,0:27:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们得换地审判了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like we'll need a change of venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.65,0:27:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把被告转移到备用地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Defendants to the backup location.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.42,0:27:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余人留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The rest stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.65,0:28:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能拖住他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hold them off as long as you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.22,0:28:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何  正义必得伸张\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and one way or another, justice will be served.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.65,0:28:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.64,0:28:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  站住别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, stop right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.68,0:28:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们站成一排  面朝法院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Line 'em up, facing the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.20,0:28:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废弃邮局  肯定就是这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Abandoned post office, this must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.07,0:28:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.35,0:28:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分头行动  清除障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Spread out, sweeping clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不定了就呼我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Give me a call if you get in over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见你  我可能得杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Next time I see you, I'll probably have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.25,0:28:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're welcome to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然现在时间紧迫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Since we appear to be out of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.94,0:28:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将放弃陪审团裁决\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we'll have to forego the jury verdict
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.93,0:28:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行即决审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and issue a summary judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.59,0:29:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信守了我们之间的协议  科利尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've upheld my end of our bargain, Mr. Collier.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.29,0:29:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我招供了  罪名成立\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I confessed, guilty as charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.42,0:29:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的革命需要流血  杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If your revolution requires blood, take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.07,0:29:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放了其他人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just please let everyone else go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.02,0:29:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐蔽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛  反击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima! Return fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.85,0:29:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在清理逃生路线  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're clearing an extraction route, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.74,0:30:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作得快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We should move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.61,0:30:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尚的自我牺牲  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Noble attempt at self-sacrifice, Harold,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.57,0:30:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但经验告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but experience has taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不要和恐怖分子谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}never to negotiate with terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.64,0:30:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的私人武装会护送你们安全回到华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My private forces will see you safely back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.28,0:30:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.39,0:30:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们二位  恐怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You two, I'm afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.68,0:30:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这里度过最后一点时光了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}will be here for the brief remainder of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.92,0:30:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经构不成威胁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's no longer a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.58,0:30:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  他不需要死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please, he doesn't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.58,0:30:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但恐怕他需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I'm afraid he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.39,0:30:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.76,0:30:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because of you, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.11,0:30:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你所造之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because of what you built.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.37,0:30:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来"时刻警惕"的人已经被解决了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like somebody already took out these Vigilance guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.03,0:31:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.97,0:31:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看来是搞不定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think I might be in over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.11,0:31:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里也分不开身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm a little busy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.86,0:31:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你那里有个巨型炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Unless you're looking at a big-ass bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.29,0:31:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设计成电力一恢复就爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}wired to blow when the power comes back on,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我这儿稳赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.43,0:31:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的机器是多么伟大的杰作  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What a piece of work is your machine, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.49,0:31:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"行动如若天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"In action, how like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.49,0:31:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}莎士比亚《哈姆雷特》
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.08,0:31:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忧思宛如上帝"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In apprehension, how like a god."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.88,0:31:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十年内  这世界将会如同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In 20 years time, life on earth will come to resemble
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.15,0:31:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古希腊的神话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the myths of the ancient Greeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.44,0:31:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由参透万物的神来照看我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A pantheon of super intelligent beings will watch over us
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.49,0:31:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用其人类代理来处理争端\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}using human agents to meddle in our affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.24,0:31:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者摧毁我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or they may simply destroy us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.27,0:31:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在自我摧毁方面也够出色了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One could argue we've done a fair job of that ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.40,0:32:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  需要有人来主控一切  不过你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Besides, someone has to be in charge, but as you well know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.65,0:32:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的诞生不易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}gods are not easily born.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.58,0:32:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想让我的神走向世人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In order to bring mine into being,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.46,0:32:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要个恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I needed a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.27,0:32:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.68,0:32:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go ahead and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木已成舟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Damage is already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.33,0:32:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚全世界的人都听到了审判间里的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Everyone in the world heard the testimony in that courtroom tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.19,0:32:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科利尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Collier,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你们所用的传输设备是谁造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}who do you think makes the equipment that you used to transmit?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的审判仅仅直播给了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your trial was broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.71,0:32:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市另一头的一间办公室里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to a single office on the other side of town
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.41,0:32:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面只有一部分电脑误导你认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}where a handful of computers led you to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.80,0:32:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界都在收看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that the whole world was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.22,0:32:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我是时候谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's high time you and I had a talk
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.72,0:32:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"的真面目了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}about the true nature of Vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.04,0:32:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我们一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't know anything about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.13,0:32:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的远超你的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I know a great deal more than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:32:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"暴政如同地狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"Tyranny, like hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.70,0:33:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会轻易被推翻"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}is not easily conquered".
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.54,0:33:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是真相信这是所谓民主吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You didn't really believe this was a democracy, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.97,0:33:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的草根运动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your grassroots movement
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.00,0:33:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就是被精心设计的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}has been meticulously planned from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.56,0:33:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  是我亲自招募的你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In fact, I recruited you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.75,0:33:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛创造的"时刻警惕"  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima created Vigilance? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.14,0:33:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的机器运作得太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your machine did it's job too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须提醒加里森参议员和他的同僚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had remind senator Garrison and his ilk
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.78,0:33:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态会多么严峻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of just how bad things could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.03,0:33:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最能提醒他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And what better way to remind them
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.61,0:33:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫过于发生在美国本土的暴行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}than a fresh atrocity on American soil?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.65,0:33:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么暴行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What atrocity?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.03,0:33:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每一次行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In all our dealings,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.87,0:33:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不曾伤及无辜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we never killed one innocent person.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.63,0:33:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.74,0:33:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  赫什  我现在过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, Hersh, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.93,0:33:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's your 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.93,0:34:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找到你老板  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just get your boss and get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.78,0:34:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫什\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hersh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.49,0:34:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here come the policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.04,0:34:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可怜的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Their poor families.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.24,0:34:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人惋惜啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.56,0:34:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你在计划什么  拜托不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whatever you're planning, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.52,0:34:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.10,0:34:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是科利尔先生  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's Mr. Collier, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.95,0:34:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走投无路之时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In a last desperate act,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.43,0:34:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你年少莽撞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}your young misguided lot
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.46,0:34:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定炸掉一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}decided to go out with a bang,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.09,0:34:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪葬的还有一大帮警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}along with a whole host of police,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.49,0:34:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记者  以及无辜市民\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}reporters, and innocent civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.94,0:34:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正历史会如此记载\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or at least that's how history will remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警察  趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}NYPD. Down on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.99,0:35:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力在恢复了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Power's coming back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.74,0:35:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫什  快离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hersh, get out of there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.26,0:35:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.67,0:35:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相迟早会浮出水面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sooner or later, the truth will come out.
