Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.26,0:35:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你的上帝和我的上帝就要决一死战了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But the time has come for your God and mine to do battle,
